<div id="review_4043706986" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4043706986" />
    <a title="Sebastian" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/27653427-sebastian"><img alt="Sebastian" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1389651884p2/27653427.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4043706986?book_show_action=true">Jul 05, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sebastian" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sebastian" href="/user/show/27653427-sebastian">Sebastian</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9789731023625" href="/book/show/17787353-citadela-autocratului">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4043706986" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2654674091504903066">2,5* <br/>I wanted to like this series more, but something didn&apos;t clicked! I don&apos;t regret reading it but i had higher expectations! Maybe i just didn&apos;t read it at the right time!</span>
  <span id="freeText2654674091504903066" style="display:none">2,5* <br />I wanted to like this series more, but something didn't clicked! I don't regret reading it but i had higher expectations! Maybe i just didn't read it at the right time!</span>
